Author: RichardStarrkey
Text: Right after the Trainspotting series I'll get to all his works. He's damn good.

Author: PM_M3_UR_SECRETS
Text: I LOVE Irvine Welsh. If you haven't yet, read "The Sex Lives Of Siamese Twins".. It's weirdly relevant to having an ED. Might be a bit triggering though. Wish I could help you on the depression thing, but I'm stuck in this shit myself so I don't know what to tell you. Hope you will get better soon.
